4. Finally, add the following lines of code just before the last </main> tag in the logged in dashboard file. Repeat for mobile:
==================================================================================
<!--This is the restart button for virtual tour-->
<section class="section pt40 pb40 virtual-tour-restart">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center">Not sure what's available in your fundraising hub? <br> Take a tour to find out.</h2>
        <p class="text-center"><a href="#" class="triggerIntroJS text-center btn btn-secondary">Start Tour</a></p>
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function(){
                $('.triggerIntroJS').click(function() {
                    introJs().start();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
<!--End virtual tour-->
==================================================================================
